                           PRIVACY POLICY FOR DICTIONARY & TRANSLATE NH-APPS
                           
- About Dictionary & Translate NH-Apps:
  Dictionary & Translate NH-Apps is a Vietnamese person who likes to write applications about dictionary,
  translation, vocabulary and English learning software.
- About my apps:
 + My app does not collect user data for any purpose other than its functionality
 + Some applications need access to memory to store data, get photos for translation.
 + Permissions to Display on other apps help the app appear on the screen, appear on other apps,
   help learn English vocabulary anytime, anywhere even when you are surfing the web, facebook.
 + Permission Accessibility or Screen Capture is a permission that every screen translation application needs 
   to be able to translate the screen, it helps the application to scan the words on the captured image for translation.
   We do not use these images for any other purpose.
 + To help apps grow, I've added ads to my apps. I would be happy if you buy the ad removal package,
   or watch the videos to remove ads

